Class TimeSlice

  • java.lang.Object
    • cs350s21project.simulation.event.TimeSlice
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable
    public class TimeSlice
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Cloneable
    Defines a timeslice descriptor, which defines the lead, trigger, and lag countdowns for servicing an event.
